    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Unified Agent 25.11.1-223 | &lt;a class="external-link" href="https://github.com/renovatebot/renovate/releases/tag/41.173.1" rel="nofollow" shape="rect"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Renovate 41.173.1&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt; | Remediate 25.10.1 | Pre-Scan Builder (PSB) 25.8.1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New Features and Updates&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a data-linked-resource-id="3713990693" data-linked-resource-type="page" data-linked-resource-version="6" href="https://docs.mend.io/integrations/latest/mend-for-bitbucket-data-center-configuration#BBDC-Scan-Settings"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;cloneSubmodules&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;feature now supports scanning a repositorys submodules via SSH as well as HTTPS.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following languages and package managers are now officially &lt;a data-linked-resource-id="3149365249" data-linked-resource-type="page" data-linked-resource-version="39" href="https://docs.mend.io/legacy-sca/latest/unified-agent-support-matrix"&gt;&lt;u&gt;supported&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Node.js 24.x (language)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;npm 11.x (package manager)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Gradle 9.x (package manager)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://docs.mend.io/integrations/latest/mend-for-bitbucket-data-center-release-notes"/>
    <published>2025-11-30T00:00:00+00:00</published>
