kage manager)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p local-id="07549598-928e-44be-bb45-865285b00857"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resolved Issues&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul local-id="193adca7-5208-46d9-b755-9f062dfb8513"&gt;&lt;li local-id="f9ce99b6-b58c-43dc-8560-ff4419d96efa"&gt;&lt;p local-id="b3ae76be-3d98-4fe3-9227-5cec6ba2b150"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(SAST)&lt;/strong&gt; Fixed an issue where SAST scans on pull requests targeting an empty main branch produced misleading results and incorrectly reported a successful scan status.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
