    <updated>2026-01-05T13:57:06.344362+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Mend Release Bot</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p local-id="87f7717c-4202-4549-b903-89853e279846"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resolved Issues&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul local-id="6aace143-8b03-4e64-a334-9bb95a6f15ed"&gt;&lt;li local-id="95d8a8a8-e283-4d21-b0f5-37ab3d9eefee"&gt;&lt;p local-id="31c72428-aa4b-46aa-8ae5-31bc592ba846"&gt;Fixed an issue where admins could not uninstall an SCM organization in certain scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li local-id="6dfc7659-9551-43d5-a677-3d56601799f9"&gt;&lt;p local-id="6b0c99cf-a610-4375-82f8-5e78318ab6ee"&gt;Fixed an issue where Renovate would open an onboarding pull request before onboarding was complete, causing the PR to be immediately closed if onboarding was not set. Now, jobs are only triggered after onboarding is finished, ensuring a smoother onboarding process.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
